An Act establishing same-day voter registration.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Section 26 of chapter 51 of the General Laws, as appearing in the 2022
2 Official Edition, is hereby amended by striking out, in line 10, the words “tenth day preceding”,
3 and inserting in place thereof the following words:- day of.
4 SECTION 2. Said section 26 of said chapter 51, as so appearing, is hereby further
5 amended by striking out, in line 11, the words “tenth day preceding”, and inserting in place
6 thereof the following words:- day of.
7 SECTION 3. Section 31 of said chapter 51 is hereby repealed.
8 SECTION 4. Section 50 of said chapter 51 is hereby repealed.
